review_text: I have been a customer for over 20 years. Great bank! Love the new london branch. Always great to see the friendly, helpful staff.
Tellers are always friendly, polite, and efficient! They kindly address you by name which adds a great personal touch.

Very very slow service drive through...
If you're between cars and can't move, you could be there
